<para style="q1">

<verse number="24" style="v" />Defend me, Yahweh my God, because of your righteousness;</para>

<para style="q1">do not let them rejoice over me.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="25" style="v" />Do not let them say in their heart, "Aha, we have what we wanted."</para>

<para style="q1">Do not let them say, "We have devoured him."</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="26" style="v" />Put them to shame and confound those who want to harm me.</para>

<para style="q1">May those who taunt me be covered with shame and dishonor.</para>
